an-super-typhoon-hainan-hits-palau/5075198|accessdate=2013-11-11|archive-date=2013-11-07|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6KxVkSGDN?url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-11-07/an-super-typhoon-hainan-hits-palau/5075198|dead-url=no}}{{en}}</ref> 當海燕繼續西移，在最東端的工業開始逐漸停產。<ref>{{cite web|author=Carl Alan Mcelroy|work=National Weather Service Office in Tiyan, Guam|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=5-11-2013|title=Tropical Storm Haiyan (31W) Advisory Number 6|url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ33-PGUM_201311041524.htm|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6KtjEz0QL?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ33-PGUM_201311041524.htm|archivedate=2013-11-05}}{{en}}</ref>當海燕在11月5日增強為颱風時，帛琉和雅浦州開始改發更高的信號。<ref>{{cite web|author=Kenneth R. Kleeschulte and Charles P. Guard|work=National Weather Service Office in Tiyan, Guam|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=5-11-2013|title=Typhoon Haiyan (31W) Advisory Number 8|url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ33-PGUM_201311050347.htm|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6KtjCfngw?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ33-PGUM_201311050347.htm|archivedate=2013-11-05}}{{en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=Patrick K. Chan|work=National Weather Service Office in Tiyan, Guam|publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration|date=5-11-2013|title=Typhoon Haiyan (31W) Advisory Number 9|url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ33-PGUM_201311051000.htm|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6KvE6Oq2w?url=http://gwydir.demon.co.uk/advisories/WTPQ33-PGUM_201311051000.htm|archivedate=2013-11-06}}{{en}}</ref> 而在帛琉[[梅萊凱奧克|梅萊凱奧克]]的政府辦事處則被用作避難所。儘管發出強制疏散令，大部分在梅萊凱奧克的居民留在島上並沒有傷亡。<ref name="ABC1">{{cite web|publisher=Australian Broadcasting Corporation|date=7-11-2013|title=Palau assesses damage after Super Typhoon Haiyan|url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2013-11-07/an-super-typhoon-hainan-hits-palau/5075198|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=htt